<br>
Any case, if you in Hate and see it drop, and no enchanters around to loot, try to find asap a chanter who needs it, and get him ported to Hate, and CoHed to your group.  This stuff is so rare that letting it rot would be a crime. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bregalad Alcarin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, High Elf Phantasmist, Xev &lt;Legends of Westwood&gt;<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.webspan.net/~scorpio/graph/mezzed.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=whittenhawkholyshroud>Whittenhawk Holyshroud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#330000>(7/2/03 9:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter - Staff of the Serpent</span><hr size=1> Bregalad,<br>
I think this must be a luck of the draw like many other epic drops. I have been in PoF at least 10 times now. Out of those 10 times the EoH has only dropped 4 times in total. and that was in 2 of the 10 trips (2 each time). So I think it is just totally random, and you just have to keep on going and trying to get it. There have been a few open raids on PoH since it was revamped, so see if you can get on one of them too. Good luck! <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=394797" target="top">Some stuff I looted in the Bazaar off of vendor bots.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
