We have done extensive killing in north part of Hate several times, killing many forsaken.   We also fought down to the south part, where tougher versions of mobs spawn, thinking that maybe forlorn revenants (lvl 56-59) will be more forthcoming, but no luck there either. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bregalad Alcarin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, High Elf Phantasmist, Xev &lt;Legends of Westwood&gt;<br>
