<br>
It's bye the bye now as PoH has been revamped, but the North side never was worth doing for drops IMO, I did it for xp once - but not a great place for that either.  The drops where too rare, that's why when I did the old hate I always cleared the South side and centre, ignoring the Northern mobs completely with the exception of those that pathed around North to South around the cathedral.<br>
<br>
I'd rather have done the wayward pathing second floor then clear all those empty corpses!  That's possibly why you've lucked out so much in the past, however since the revamp i've not been there at all.  Good luck when you next go <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
